<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grandio Greenhouses - Transform Your Garden Dreams Into Reality</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@300;400;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --forest: #1a3d2e;
            --moss: #4a7c59;
            --sage: #8ba888;
            --cream: #f5f1e8;
            --terracotta: #d4773c;
            --sky: #a8c5d4;
            --soil: #2d2416;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--soil);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream) 0%, #e8e4d9 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Organic Background Pattern */
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -20%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 150%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, 
                rgba(138, 168, 136, 0.15) 0%, 
                transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30%;
            left: -15%;
            width: 60%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, 
                rgba(74, 124, 89, 0.08) 0%, 
                transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 25s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
            33% { transform: translate(30px, -40px) rotate(5deg); }
            66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) rotate(-3deg); }
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem 5%;
            animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--forest);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--forest);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--terracotta);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--moss);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Hero Content */
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 5%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
        }

        .hero-text {
            animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-out 0.3s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInLeft {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--moss);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            background: rgba(74, 124, 89, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.5s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--forest);
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: var(--moss);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .highlight::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 8px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 12px;
            background: var(--terracotta);
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: expand 1.2s ease-out 0.8s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes expand {
            from { width: 0; }
            to { width: 100%; }
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--soil);
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 540px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.7s backwards;
        }

        .trust-badges {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.9s backwards;
        }

        .badge {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--forest);
        }

        .badge-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: var(--moss);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 1.1s backwards;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 1.1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--forest);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(26, 61, 46, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(26, 61, 46, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--forest);
            border: 2px solid var(--forest);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--forest);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Hero Visual */
        .hero-visual {
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeInRight 1s ease-out 0.5s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInRight {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        .greenhouse-container {
            position: relative;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .greenhouse-frame {
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 
                0 20px 60px rgba(26, 61, 46, 0.15),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(74, 124, 89, 0.1);
            transform: rotate(-2deg);
            animation: tilt 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes tilt {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-2deg); }
            50% { transform: rotate(2deg); }
        }

        .greenhouse-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sage) 0%, var(--moss) 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Decorative greenhouse illustration */
        .greenhouse-image::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 40%;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26, 61, 46, 0.3), transparent);
        }

        .greenhouse-image::after {
            content: 'GRANDIO';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            letter-spacing: 8px;
        }

        .floating-badge {
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            padding: 1.2rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: floatBadge 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes floatBadge {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }

        .badge-top {
            top: -20px;
            right: -20px;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .badge-bottom {
            bottom: -20px;
            left: -20px;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }

        .badge-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--forest);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .badge-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--moss);
        }

        /* Decorative elements */
        .leaf-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: var(--sage);
            opacity: 0.15;
            border-radius: 0 100% 0 100%;
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .leaf-1 { top: 10%; left: 5%; animation-duration: 25s; }
        .leaf-2 { top: 60%; right: 8%; animation-duration: 30s; animation-direction: reverse; }
        .leaf-3 { bottom: 15%; left: 15%; animation-duration: 35s; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 968px) {
            .hero-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding-top: 2rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .greenhouse-frame {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }

            .floating-badge {
                position: static;
                margin: 1rem 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .hero-description {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .btn {
                text-align: center;
            }

            nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero">
        <!-- Decorative leaves -->
        <div class="leaf-decoration leaf-1"></div>
        <div class="leaf-decoration leaf-2"></div>
        <div class="leaf-decoration leaf-3"></div>

        <!-- Navigation -->
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">GRANDIO</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/greenhouses/">Greenhouses</a></li>
                <li><a href="/product-category/accessories/">Accessories</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact_and_faq/">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- Hero Content -->
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <span class="eyebrow">Premium Aluminum Greenhouses</span>
                
                <h1>
                    Transform Your<br>
                    <span class="highlight">Garden Dreams</span><br>
                    Into Reality
                </h1>

                <p class="hero-description">
                    Professional-grade aluminum greenhouses engineered for year-round growing. 
                    Built with passion in Idaho, trusted by gardeners nationwide since 2012.
                </p>

                <div class="trust-badges">
                    <div class="badge">
                        <span class="badge-icon">✓</span>
                        <span>Lifetime Frame Warranty</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="badge">
                        <span class="badge-icon">✓</span>
                        <span>Free Shipping</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="badge">
                        <span class="badge-icon">✓</span>
                        <span>12+ Years Experience</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/greenhouses/" class="btn btn-primary">View Greenhouses</a>
                    <a href="/greenhouse-catalog-request/" class="btn btn-secondary">Free Catalog</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-visual">
                <div class="greenhouse-container">
                    <div class="greenhouse-frame">
                        <div class="greenhouse-image"></div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="floating-badge badge-top">
                        <div class="badge-title">From $1,099</div>
                        <div class="badge-subtitle">Price Match Guarantee</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="floating-badge badge-bottom">
                        <div class="badge-title">Made in USA</div>
                        <div class="badge-subtitle">Idaho Built Quality</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
